## Widget Props

### RefreshableContent<T>

| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `state` | `BaseState<T>` | State from notifier |
| `onRefresh` | `Future<void> Function()` | Refresh callback |
| `childBuilder` | `Widget Function(T data)` | Build content |
| `onRetry` | `VoidCallback?` | Error retry callback |
| `emptyWidget` | `Widget?` | Empty state widget |
| `isEmpty` | `bool Function(T)?` | Custom empty check |

### PaginatedListView<T>

| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `state` | `PaginatedState<T>` | State from notifier |
| `onRefresh` | `Future<void> Function()` | Refresh (page 1) |
| `onLoadMore` | `Future<void> Function()?` | Load next page |
| `itemBuilder` | `Widget Function(BuildContext, T, int)` | Build item |
| `emptyWidget` | `Widget?` | Empty state widget |
| `scrollController` | `ScrollController?` | Optional controller |
| `padding` | `EdgeInsets?` | List padding |
| `loadMoreThreshold` | `double` | Trigger threshold (0.9) |

