## Key Behaviors

### Initial Load
- Shows full-screen loading spinner
- Use `addPostFrameCallback` in `initState`

### Refresh (Pull-to-Refresh)
- Shows refresh indicator
- **Keeps previous data visible** (not spinner)
- For paginated: **Always resets to page 1**

### Load More (Paginated)
- Triggered at 90% scroll
- Shows loading at bottom
- Appends new items

### Error State
- Shows error message with retry button
- Previous data preserved if available

