## State Classes

### BaseState<T>

```dart
BaseState.initial()           // Before first load
BaseState.loading()           // Initial loading
BaseState.loaded(T data)      // Has data
BaseState.error(String msg)   // Error occurred
```

### PaginatedState<T>

```dart
PaginatedState.initial()                        // Before first load
PaginatedState.loading()                        // Initial loading
PaginatedState.loaded(PaginatedList<T> data)   // Has data
PaginatedState.loadingMore(PaginatedList<T>)   // Loading next page
PaginatedState.error(String msg)               // Error occurred
```

### PaginatedList<T>

```dart
PaginatedList(
  items: List<T>,
  currentPage: int,
  lastPage: int,
  perPage: int,
  total: int,
)

// Getters
paginatedList.hasMore     // More pages exist
paginatedList.isFirstPage // On first page
paginatedList.isEmpty     // No items

// Methods
paginatedList.appendPage(newPage)  // Merge pages
```

