## Common Mistakes

### ❌ Wrong: Non-scrollable child

```dart
RefreshIndicator(
  onRefresh: () async {},
  child: Column(children: [...]), // Not scrollable!
)
```

### ✅ Correct: Scrollable child

```dart
RefreshableContent<Data>(
  state: state,
  childBuilder: (data) => SingleChildScrollView(
    child: Column(children: [...]),
  ),
)
```

### ❌ Wrong: Load current page on refresh

```dart
onRefresh: () => loadPage(currentPage), // Wrong for pagination
```

### ✅ Correct: Reset to page 1

```dart
onRefresh: () => load(), // PaginatedNotifier.load() always loads page 1
```

