## Checklist

- [ ] Extend `BaseNotifier<T>` or `PaginatedNotifier<T>`
- [ ] Use `RefreshableContent<T>` or `PaginatedListView<T>`
- [ ] Initial load in `initState` with `addPostFrameCallback`
- [ ] Typed convenience methods on notifier
- [ ] Empty widget for empty state
- [ ] All strings use `AppLocalizations`
